QuestData.Title: Veteran Reinforcements
QuestData.Description:
Commander Lethanak was insightful, as always. We will need the help of our most veteran guards to stop their threat. Rallying them was the perfect task for a young cadet like Sendrax, but she may need support.
Sendrax's path will take her towards the west, which may have been overwhelmed by this rising threat. They will need aid as well. Take this concoction and give them your support.
QuestData.LogDescription: Help the injured guards and find Sendrax.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Meet Sendrax at the Conservatory Outpost.
QuestData.RewardText:
Sendrax stopped by and rushed through. That one is a whirlwind.
I like her.

Objectives.Objective: Meet Sendrax at the Conservatory Outpost
